issue.title: Development
issue.body:
**SoundMap.java:** Added optimize() function to allow for key binding and Map renaming.

**MapOptimization.java:** _Most likely needs work._  Should be able to point two different Maps to the same Map object - the one being bound to the key and another one, so they represent the same object.  Same story for renaming.  toggleKeys() can tell you which HashMap to implement for the keyboard mapping depending on user input.

issue.title: Development
issue.body:
**SoundMap.java:** Allows for optimization of SoundMap by allowing to toggle hotkeys and new names.

**MapOptimization.java:** Needs work...desperately...Currently seems like it allows binding numerical keys to certain maps, assigning a new name **once** to each map, and suggesting that user can activate key to implement new map of key bindings.

issue.title: Create sound HashMap for KeyCode to file name
issue.body:
HashMap maps KeyCodes for all available keys on keyboard to corresponding sound bites.
map() function must be called to finalize map.
filepaths must be inserted into filepaths array first.

issue.title: Working dropdown menu, extension checker
issue.body:
**Autocomplete.java:** When initialized, permits autocomplete functionality (scrapped from main design, possible optimization?)

**Dropdown.java:** Old dropdown menu - does not permit filtering, does permit selection.

**ExtensionChecker.java:** When initialized, permits functionality to check that file extensions are valid.

**FilterDropdownMenu.java:** Dropdown menu, permits filtering and selection, minor bug: menu appears even after selection.
